8    # Private so h2py ignored it
9    def __HRESULT_FROM_WIN32(x: int) -> int:
10       return x if x <= 0 else ((x & 0x0000FFFF) | (FACILITY_WIN32 << 16) | -2147483648)
11   
12   
13   def __HRESULT_FROM_SETUPAPI(x: int):
14       APPLICATION_ERROR_MASK = 0x20000000  # From winnt.h
15       ERROR_SEVERITY_ERROR = -1073741824  # From winnt.h
16       return (
17           ((x & 0x0000FFFF) | (FACILITY_SETUPAPI << 16) | -2147483648)
18           if (
19               (x & (APPLICATION_ERROR_MASK | ERROR_SEVERITY_ERROR))
20               == (APPLICATION_ERROR_MASK | ERROR_SEVERITY_ERROR)
21           )
22           else HRESULT_FROM_WIN32(x)
23       )
